<section id="mobile-push-android" role="topic">
    <sectioninfo>
        <abstract>
            <para>Describes how to set up &GCMlong; to send a push notification to a mobile endpoint using &SNS;.</para>
        </abstract>
    </sectioninfo>
    <title id="mobile-push-android.title">Setting Up Android Push Notifications</title>
    <para>This section describes how you can create an Android app to receive push notifications.
        The platform notification services you can use for push notifications on Android are
        &FCMlong; (&FCM;) and its predecessor, &GCMlong; (&GCM;). </para>
